= Template Sample =

Templates are a tool for adding boilerplate text and meta data to new items. They are useful when a wiki will have many pages with a similar format.

Under MoinMoin 2, any item having the tag `template` is a template. Under MoinMoin 1.9.x, any page ending in `Template` was a template.

Templates are specific to a content type. This template can only be used to create new `text/x.moin.wiki` items. To use this template, create a new moin wiki item and choose the link with the template's name rather than the `create this item from scratch` link.

